snippet.title: Newzee
snippet.description:
Are you interested in the current affairs and the happenings of your country? Want to watch what is happening now arround the world? What leaders  and celebrities are doing? then it is the right place to be!

I am associated with media industry from past two decades, after working both in electronic and print journalism I'm entering now in the world of social media. 

Here in NEWZEE you can find the latest news videos, opinion pieces, animations and series content from arround the globe. We are also covering world events, sports, entertainment, technology, motoring, food, fashion, beauty, travel and muh more. In future you can also have Headline, Bulletin, and Breaking News.

Check out our playlists to view the latest videos and don't forget to subscribe to our YouTube channel NEWZEE for daily video updates.

Subscribe to our channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVraSltSET7CHmEulDTqMXA

Visit the NEWZEE website: http://www.newzee.today/
